our weeks apart.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Serological evidence of immunity </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Australian Immunisation Register (AIR) history of previous varicella infection</span></p>', 1, 0, '2025-01-08 11:20:02', '2025-01-08 10:21:05'),
(13, 2, 11, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">Influenza </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Annual Influenza Vaccination</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">: Healthcare workers must receive a flu vaccine each year, especially if working in high-risk areas (e.g., aged care, ICU, or with immunocompromised patients).</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Workers in Category A positions in NSW Health facilities must be vaccinated prior to 1 June each year.</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence Required: </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #00b0f0;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence of an annual flu vaccine given prior to 1 June each year<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp; </span></span></p>', 1, 0, '2025-01-08 11:20:02', '2025-01-08 10:23:48'),
(14, 2, 12, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">COVID-19</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">As of <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">May 2024</strong>, the <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">COVID-19 vaccine mandate</strong> for healthcare workers in <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">New South Wales (NSW)</strong> has been <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">revoked</strong>.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Despite this, individual healthcare facilities may still choose to implement their own policies regarding COVID-19 vaccination depending on their risk assessments and workplace safety regulations‚Äã</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span><a style=\"color: #0662bb !important; text-decoration: underline !important; font-weight: 800 !important;\" href=\"https://www.tga.gov.au/products/covid-19/covid-19-vaccines/international-covid-19-vaccines-recognised-australia\" target=\"_blank\" >TGA Gov Au International COVID-19 vaccines recognised by Australia </a><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #00b0f0; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #00b0f0; background: white;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence Required: </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">COVID-19 Primary dose 1&amp;2 and COVID-19 dose 3/Booster </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Proof of a temporary or permanent medical exemption.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 107%; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></p>', 1, 0, '2025-01-08 11:22:24', '2025-03-12 12:09:45'),
(15, 2, 13, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">Diphtheria, Tetanus, Pertussis (dTpa)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Since healthcare workers are required to have protection against all three&mdash;diphtheria, tetanus, and pertussis (dTpa)&mdash;the ADT vaccine alone is not sufficient or acceptable.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Pertussis serology: Serological testing is not considered a reliable or valid method for determining immunity to pertussis.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence Required: </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Proof of a single dose of dTpa vaccine within the last 10 years.</span></p>', 1, 0, '2025-01-08 11:22:24', '2025-01-08 10:23:26'),
(16, 2, 14, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\">Hepatitis A</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><a style=\"color: #0662bb !important; text-decoration: underline !important; font-weight: 800 !important;\" href=\"https://immunisationhandbook.health.gov.au/contents/vaccine-preventable-diseases/hepatitis-a\" target=\"_blank\">Health Gov Au Hepatitis A immunisation handbook </a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">In <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">New South Wales (NSW)</strong>, the <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">Hepatitis A vaccine</strong> is <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">not mandatory</strong> for all healthcare workers but is recommended for those in <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">high-risk roles</strong>. These roles include healthcare workers who frequently work in or with <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">Indigenous communities</strong>, particularly in rural or remote areas.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence Required:</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence of two doses of vaccine</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Serological evidence of immunity </span></p>', 1, 0, '2025-01-08 11:25:16', '2025-03-12 12:23:37'),
(17, 2, 15, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\">Tuberculosis (TB):</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><a style=\"color: #0662bb !important; text-decoration: underline !important; font-weight: 800 !important;\"href=\"https://www.health.nsw.gov.au/Infectious/tuberculosis/Pages/default.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">NSW Gov Health Tuberculosis</a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: 8.0pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">TB screening is mandatory for healthcare workers in high-risk roles, including nurses, as part of the Occupational Assessment, Screening, and Vaccination Policy.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence Required: </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Proof of a BCG vaccination</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Interferon Gamma Release Assay (IGRA) blood test, such as QuantiFERON-TB Gold</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Mantoux test</span><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"> / T</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">uberculin skin test (TST)</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">TB screening</span><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">questionnaire</span></p>', 1, 0, '2025-01-08 11:25:16', '2025-03-12 12:25:38'),
(18, 2, 16, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\">Polio</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><a style=\"color: #0662bb !important; text-decoration: underline !important; font-weight: 800 !important;\" href=\"https://immunisationhandbook.health.gov.au/recommendations/healthcare-workers-who-may-have-contact-with-people-with-polio-are-recommended-to-receive-booster-doses-of-ipv-containing-vaccine-every-10-years\" target=\"_blank\">Health Gov Au Polio immunisation handbook</a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Polio vaccination is generally <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">recommended</strong> but not <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">mandatory</strong> for healthcare workers, including nurses and midwives, across all states. Each state follows the guidelines in the Australian Immunisation Handbook, which recommends a booster dose of the inactivated poliovirus (IPV) every 10 years for healthcare workers who may come into contact with polio.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">These recommendations are based on occupational risk, with no strict statewide mandates for polio vaccination in healthcare settings, but individual facilities may set specific policies for high-risk exposure roles. For more guidance, see the Australian Immunisation Handbook&rsquo;s section on healthcare worker vaccinations.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence Required:</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Proof of receiving the inactivated polio vaccine (IPV)</span><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">often recorded in (AIR)</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Serological evidence of immunity (Antibody Test)</span></p>', 1, 0, '2025-01-08 11:27:35', '2025-03-12 12:26:58'),
(19, 3, 8, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\">Hepatitis B</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><a style=\"color: #0662bb !important; text-decoration: underline !important; font-weight: 800 !important;\"href=\"https://www.health.vic.gov.au/infectious-diseases/hepatitis-b\" target=\"_blank\">Health VIC Gov Hepatitis B</a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence Required: </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\">Completion of the Hepatitis B vaccination series (3 doses) <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">AND</strong> <span style=\"background: white;\">surface antibody level &gt; 10 mIU/mL) </span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><a style=\"color: #0662bb !important; text-decoration: underline !important; font-weight: 800 !important;\" href=\"https://immunisationhandbook.health.gov.au/resources/tables/table-monovalent-hepatitis-b-vaccines-for-adolescents-and-adults\" target=\"_blank\" >Hepatitis B vaccination schedule: </a><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\">s<span style=\"background: white;\">econd dose 1 month after the first dose, and third dose 6 months after the first dose.</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">After the completion of the three-dose series, workers are required to undergo a <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">serological test</strong> to confirm immunity (Hepatitis B surface antibody level greater than 10 mIU/mL).</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">In some cases, a <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">booster dose</strong> may be recommended if the immunity levels decrease over time or if the worker does not achieve sufficient antibody levels after the initial series</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\">if an applicant receives a Hepatitis B vaccine but does not produce sufficient antibodies (non-convertor), they might not be allowed to work in a role that requires immunity to the virus.</span></strong></p>', 1, 0, '2025-01-08 11:28:17', '2025-03-12 12:33:50'),
(20, 3, 9, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">Measles, Mumps, Rubella (MMR)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Mandatory for applicants born during or since 1966.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence Required: </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence of two doses of MMR vaccine, administered at least four weeks apart, with both doses given after the individual is 12 months of age.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Serological evidence of immunity</span></p>', 1, 0, '2025-01-08 11:28:17', '2025-01-08 10:30:41'),
(21, 3, 10, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">Varicella (Chickenpox)</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence Required: </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence of two doses of varicella-containing vaccine, given at least four weeks apart.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Serological evidence of immunity (positive IgG result)</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Australian Immunisation Register (AIR) history of previous varicella infection</span></p>', 1, 0, '2025-01-10 06:07:52', '2025-01-10 05:09:07'),
(22, 3, 11, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; color: #0070c0; background: white;\">Influenza </span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">In <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">Victoria</strong>, the <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">Influenza (flu) vaccine</strong> is <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">mandatory</strong> for healthcare workers, including nurses and midwives, who have direct patient contact in public and private hospitals, aged care, and ambulance services. The flu vaccine must be administered annually, typically before the <strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\">15th of August</strong> each year. This is to protect healthcare workers and vulnerable patients from influenza outbreaks.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">If healthcare workers do not comply with the flu vaccination requirement, they may face work restrictions or be reassigned to other roles within the health service</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: 107%;\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence Required:&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent: -.25in; line-height: 107%; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;\"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"mso-list: Ignore;\">&bull;<span style=\"font: 7.0pt \'Times New Roman\';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; mso-fareast-font-family: Arial; background: white;\">Evidence of an annual flu vaccine given prior to 15 August each year<span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>', 1, 0, '2025-01-10 06:07:52', '2025-01-10 05:09:07');
